Previous section: @{"Acknowledgements" link "Acknowledgements" 0}


@{b}Program History@{ub}

- Version 1.0ß1 (22-Oct-96, beta release)
· First version.

- Version 1.0ß2 (21-Jan-97, beta release)
· Can now be interrupted with Ctrl-C when run from Shell;
· Added "dirname" as a shortcut for "dirname/#?"
· Workbench window now centres horizontally on any screen;
· Small bug in ASL file selector code fixed;
· Errors flash only the WB screen now, instead of all screens;
· Code to handle ID errors from Workbench tidied up;
· AppIcons are now rejected.  Previously, would be IDd as dirs;
· Window changed from SMART to SIMPLE refresh.

- Version 1.0 (24-Mar-97, public release)
· Public release of 1.0ß2.
· Some extra checks in Workbench startup/closedown code added.


Next section: @{"Legal Matters" link "Legal" 0}

